A nice "Zwischenzug". This kind of move is always hard to spot, since if you take a whole piece of the board, somehow your attention gets focused on that piece exchange. My opponent told me he liked this move. I could not find out how to respond to his resignation note, so I decided to annotate the game. The rest of the game is not important anymore.
